  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">SRM- show config</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Code Example">show config</text> prints the full configuration table: the SRM and PALcode versions; the processor (Alpha EV6 pass 1, 268 MHz); core logic (Cchip 21272-CA, Dchip 21272-DA, Pchip 21272-EA, TIG / Arbiter Rev 7.31); the memory array; the PCI hose (the Cypress 82C693 bridge and IDE at bus 0, slot 5); and the ISA device list (MOUSE, KBD, COM1, COM2, LPT1, FLOPPY with their base addresses and IRQs). A full sample is in Example - Performance.</para>
